stmt.name: create_events
stmt.sql: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS events (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT, stamp TIMESTAMP, `interval` INTEGER)

stmt.name: select_1
stmt.sql: SELECT * FROM events WHERE stamp + INTERVAL `interval` MICROSECOND < NOW()
